A/C: Julien RAKOTOAARIJAONA
___________________________


Nijotso tambony ty tany oa, ilay zanak’andriamanitsy e e e!
Niavy hagnavotsy antsika oa, izay ro foto-diany ee e!
Tsy tafapetra tan-tragnon-dRy Babany, izay niadagnany
Fa niavy tetoy, an-tany etoy, ie Kristy.


Tsy nifingy volo’olo na nagnavakavaky
Ndre mahantra na mpagnarivo, samy novangiany ee e!
Samby nomeny fagnantenà handova lagnitsy
Samby handray, eo amin’ny Ray, mandrakizay


Fe mbo noenjehy avao, nosianambotse
Le nivonoa, manahaky ty mpangalatse
Kanefa tsy nanan-keloka, na nanampahotà
Fa tena anak’Andriamanintse, lelehy tokana


Ie ro nampianatsy antsika mba hifamela heloka ee e!
Tsy hifanao an-dolom-po na koa hifampiavgna ee e!
Hifampizara hafalia, sy fitiavana
Ho iraika avao, sy hifandray, ty tsirairay.


Ie nanao fahagagà tetoy , tamin’ny fampikarana ee e!
Nanova ty rano ho divay koa Ie ho famantaranaee e!
Fa Ia nahazo ty fahefà, baka an-danitsy
Avy amin’ny Ray, mandrakizay, mandrakizay.